{"name":"Skillful Defender","type":"ability","img":"modules/hyperborea-compendium/assets/icons/ability.png","system":{"description":"<div class=\"page\" title=\"Page 46\">\n<div class=\"layoutArea\">\n<div class=\"column\">\n<p>To avail armour to its utmost. When clad in medium or heavy armour, the cataphract gains a +1 AC bonus from 1st to 6th levels, and a +2 AC bonus from 7th to 12th levels.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>","autoTags":[],"manualTags":[],"save":"","pattern":"transparent","requirements":"cataphract","roll":"","rollType":"result","rollTarget":null,"blindroll":false,"tags":[]},"effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.3lf4GUXDq7VDYsoZ"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"hyperborea","systemVersion":"1.000","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1679249969686,"modifiedTime":1681579175792,"lastModifiedBy":"Sp6Zt9CdjPzQ3Qea"},"_id":"909FrdPIrYDyQEuD","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"Sp6Zt9CdjPzQ3Qea":3}}
{"name":"Shield Sacrifice","type":"ability","img":"modules/hyperborea-compendium/assets/icons/ability.png","system":{"description":"<div class=\"page\" title=\"Page 46\">\n<div class=\"layoutArea\">\n<div class=\"column\">\n<p>To sacrifice a shield and escape harm from a single melee blow. When wielding a shield in combat, if the cataphract is struck by a melee blow, the player may opt to announce a <em>shield sacrifice</em> to avoid damage; however, the shield is destroyed by the blow. If the shield is magical, it has a chance-in-eight to survive destruction equal to the shield&rsquo;s bonus (e.g., a <strong>+1 small shield</strong> has a 1-in-8 chance of surviving destruction). This ability cannot be used after damage is rolled, and is usable but once per day, regardless of results.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>","autoTags":[],"manualTags":[],"save":"","pattern":"transparent","requirements":"cataphract","roll":"","rollType":"result","rollTarget":null,"blindroll":false,"tags":[]},"effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.3lf4GUXDq7VDYsoZ"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"hyperborea","systemVersion":"1.000","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1679249969686,"modifiedTime":1681579175792,"lastModifiedBy":"Sp6Zt9CdjPzQ3Qea"},"_id":"NlNROwUQmmDS5GMC","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"Sp6Zt9CdjPzQ3Qea":3}}
{"name":"Weapon Mastery","type":"ability","img":"modules/hyperborea-compendium/assets/icons/ability.png","system":{"description":"<div class=\"page\" title=\"Page 46\">\n<div class=\"layoutArea\">\n<div class=\"column\">\n<p><em>Mastery</em> of the lance and one other weapon (+1 &ldquo;to hit&rdquo; and +1 damage). Additional weapons may be mastered at 4th, 8th, and 12th levels. As noted in <strong>Chapter 6: Equipment</strong>, the attack rate for melee weapons and the rates of fire for most missile weapons improve through weapon mastery. For more information on weapon mastery, see <strong>Chapter 9: Combat</strong>, <em>weapon skill</em>.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>","autoTags":[],"manualTags":[],"save":"","pattern":"transparent","requirements":"cataphract","roll":"","rollType":"result","rollTarget":0,"blindroll":false,"tags":[]},"effects":[],"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"hyperborea","systemVersion":"1.000","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1679250294860,"modifiedTime":1681579175793,"lastModifiedBy":"Sp6Zt9CdjPzQ3Qea"},"_id":"XY7YJUOQmeqhM27n","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"Sp6Zt9CdjPzQ3Qea":3}}
