{"name":"Mounted Charge","type":"ability","img":"modules/hyperborea-compendium/assets/icons/ability.png","system":{"description":"<div class=\"page\" title=\"Page 46\">\n<div class=\"layoutArea\">\n<div class=\"column\">\n<p>A thunderous mounted onset both feared and renowned. The cataphract&rsquo;s lance charge from horseback or camelback is at +2 to the attack roll (+3 versus footmen) and treble damage dice (other modifiers added afterwards, such as strength, weapon mastery, etc.).</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>","autoTags":[],"manualTags":[],"save":"","pattern":"transparent","requirements":"cataphract","roll":"","rollType":"result","rollTarget":null,"blindroll":false,"tags":[]},"effects":[],"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.3lf4GUXDq7VDYsoZ"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"hyperborea","systemVersion":"1.000","coreVersion":"10.291","createdTime":1679249969686,"modifiedTime":1681579175792,"lastModifiedBy":"Sp6Zt9CdjPzQ3Qea"},"_id":"i7zQl4ctiOiEz5JV","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"Sp6Zt9CdjPzQ3Qea":3}}
